Requirements Version 2
Best Buyâ€“Style Electronics E-Commerce System

Functional Requirements:
- register with email verification
- login using secure authentication
- browse and search electronic products
- compare product specifications
- add and remove items from shopping cart
- make secure online payments
- track orders in real time
- Admins can be able to manage products, pricing, and promotions
- Admins would be able to monitor inventory levels
- Administrators can manage customer orders

Non-Functional Requirements:
- System must support high traffic during sales
- Page load time must be under 3 seconds
- Payment transactions must be encrypted
- System availability must be 99.9%
- System must be scalable
- System must ensure data privacy
